title: Bug 121687: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table within a grid cell
description: When trying to export data from a table that is inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
OB: When attempting to export data from a table within a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
EB: The data should be exported successfully without any exceptions.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Insert a grid. 
2. Insert a table into one of the grid cells. 
3. Insert another table into a different grid cell.
